getTraversalPlayers

private java.util.Collection<org.tmapi.core.Topic> getTraversalPlayers(org.tmapi.core.Topic topic,
                                                                       org.tmapi.core.Topic associationType,
                                                                       org.tmapi.core.Topic roleType,
                                                                       org.tmapi.core.Topic otherRoleType)
Method extract the traversal players of the given topic. The associationType represents the type of considered association items. The roleType represents the type of the role the given topic has to play, if it is null the roleType will be ignored. The otherRoleType is the role type the traversal player has to play, if it is null it will be ignored.

Parameters:
topic - the topic
associationType - the type of considered associations or null
roleType - the role type of the given topic or null
otherRoleType - the role type of the traversal player or null
Returns:
a collection of all traversal players
